---smd
title: "Whistle characterization of long-beaked common dolphin (Delphinus delphis bairdii) in La Paz Bay, Gulf of California"
authors:
  - name: "Óscar Carlón-Beltrán"
    affiliation: "Department of Marine and Coastal Sciences, Autonomous University of Baja California Sur, La Paz, Baja California Sur, Mexico"
